window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Craig Johnson has won multiple awards and earned starred reviews from <i>Library Journal,</i> <i>Publishers Weekly,</i> and <i>Kirkus Reviews</i> for his <i>New York Times</i> best-selling Walt Longmire mysteries. Embarking on his eighth adventure in <i>As the Crow Flies,</i> Sheriff Longmire is searching the Cheyenne Reservation for a site to host his daughter’s wedding, when he sees a woman fall to her death. Teaming up with beautiful tribal chief Lolo Long, Walt sets out to investigate the suspicious death.</p>"; 
